  "title": "Recycle/Shred Event | Raleigh Hills Business Association",
  "description": "SAVE THE DATE Our 14th Annual Recycle/Shred Event will be April 18, 2026 We will be having our event from 9am to Noon in the AAA Parking lot on 8555 SW Apple Way, PDX 97225 RHBA Sponsored Shred truck from Shred NW Secure shred for a maximum of THREE bags or boxes",
  "htmlMain": "<div id=\"pl-3256\" class=\"panel-layout\"><div id=\"pg-3256-0\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"><div id=\"pgc-3256-0-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\"><div id=\"panel-3256-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\"><div class=\"textwidget\"><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">SAVE THE DATE</h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Our 14th Annual Recycle/Shred Event will be April 18, 2026</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone  wp-image-4509\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2026-Recycle-Sponsors-banner-V2-300x262.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2026-Recycle-Sponsors-banner-V2-300x262.jpg 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2026-Recycle-Sponsors-banner-V2-100x87.jpg 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2026-Recycle-Sponsors-banner-V2-150x131.jpg 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2026-Recycle-Sponsors-banner-V2-200x175.jpg 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2026-Recycle-Sponsors-banner-V2-450x393.jpg 450w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2026-Recycle-Sponsors-banner-V2.jpg 457w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 381px) 100vw, 381px\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">We will be having our event from 9am to Noon in the AAA Parking lot on 8555 SW Apple Way, PDX 97225</h2>\n<h2 class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1251 aligncenter\" style=\"text-align: center;\">RHBA Sponsored Shred truck from Shred NW</h2>\n<h3><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Secure shred for a maximum of THREE bags or boxes PER vehicle. More than 3 boxes? Please make a donation to over the cost of your extra shred items. To support this event cash donations will be accepted.&nbsp;</strong></h3>\n<h2 class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1251 aligncenter\" style=\"text-align: center;\">- Scan this QR Code or use this <a href=\"https://buy.stripe.com/7sIeWN4SPepXcaQcN4\">Donation Link</a></h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4312 aligncenter\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/qr-code-Shred-Event-sponsor-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/qr-code-Shred-Event-sponsor-300x300.jpg 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/qr-code-Shred-Event-sponsor-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/qr-code-Shred-Event-sponsor-150x150.jpg 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/qr-code-Shred-Event-sponsor-768x768.jpg 768w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/qr-code-Shred-Event-sponsor-100x100.jpg 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/qr-code-Shred-Event-sponsor-200x200.jpg 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/qr-code-Shred-Event-sponsor-450x450.jpg 450w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/qr-code-Shred-Event-sponsor-600x600.jpg 600w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/qr-code-Shred-Event-sponsor-900x900.jpg 900w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/qr-code-Shred-Event-sponsor-280x280.jpg 280w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/qr-code-Shred-Event-sponsor.jpg 1155w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 160px) 100vw, 160px\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: center;\">This year these Member business will be taking recycle/shred:\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: center;\">SBC Recycle - accepting eWaste&nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.sbcrecycle.com/\">Electronic Recycling Data Destruction&nbsp; SBC Recycle</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: center;\">Community Warehouse will be accepting usable home-goods&nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.communitywarehouse.org/\">Home - Community Warehouse</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: center;\">Garden Home/West Slope Community Libraries will be taking bottles and cans&nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gardenhomelibrary.org/\">Garden Home and West Slope Community Libraries</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: center;\">Neighborhood House with Two Can Tuesday&nbsp; canned - nonperishable food items; pet food; menstrual &amp; hygiene products&nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"https://nhpdx.org/\">Home - Neighborhood House</a></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: center;\">'\n<ul>\n<li>RHBA Member James Recycling will be accepting items the same day at the New Seasons Milwaukie Store.&nbsp; <a href=\"https://jshrecycling.com/\">Home - James Recycling</a>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4294\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4294\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-4294\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/stick-figure-tandem-bike-vector-id177457325-587806983-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/stick-figure-tandem-bike-vector-id177457325-587806983-300x201.jpg 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/stick-figure-tandem-bike-vector-id177457325-587806983-100x67.jpg 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/stick-figure-tandem-bike-vector-id177457325-587806983-150x101.jpg 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/stick-figure-tandem-bike-vector-id177457325-587806983-200x134.jpg 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/stick-figure-tandem-bike-vector-id177457325-587806983-450x302.jpg 450w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/stick-figure-tandem-bike-vector-id177457325-587806983-600x403.jpg 600w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/stick-figure-tandem-bike-vector-id177457325-587806983-280x188.jpg 280w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/stick-figure-tandem-bike-vector-id177457325-587806983-272x182.jpg 272w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/stick-figure-tandem-bike-vector-id177457325-587806983.jpg 612w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" loading=\"lazy\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4294\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tandem Recycling Event: Same Day/Same Time</figcaption></figure></li>\n<li></li>\n<li>Valley Community Presbyterian will be have their own recycle event: it's an opportunity to park your car and walk through and talk to the different earth friendly business from the greater Portland area&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.valleycommunity.org/events\">Events — Valley Community Presbyterian</a></li>\n<li></li>\n<li>Questions or concerns or to volunteer contact: Bev Snow-Kuehn 503.452.0071 or send a message to info@RaleighHillsBusinessAssn.org</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-3256-1\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"><div id=\"pgc-3256-1-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\"><div id=\"panel-3256-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\"><div class=\"textwidget\"><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Recap of Our 13th Annual Shred Event 4/26/25</h2>\n<h4 class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1251 aligncenter\">The tally of donations:</h4>\n<h4 class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1251 aligncenter\">310 Cars: We also received generous cash donations from some of the 310 cars that showed up, showing their appreciation for our organization and what we bring to the community.</h4>\n<h4 class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1251 aligncenter\">SBC: 3500 lbs of electronics, batteries and lights</h4>\n<h4 class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1251 aligncenter\">Community Warehouse: 2 trucks were necessary to accept all the donations</h4>\n<h4 class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1251 aligncenter\">Friends of West Slope Library: 2 cars were full of bottles and cans for recycling</h4>\n<h4 class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1251 aligncenter\">Shred NW: 76 roll carts totaling 11,390 lbs of shred</h4>\n<h4 class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1251 aligncenter\">Neighborhood House: 885 lbs of groceries (small SUV filled with canned goods, etc)</h4>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 150%;\">Thank you to our generous sponsors who helped defray the cost of our 2025 Shred Truck Rental</p>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-3256-2\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"><div id=\"pgc-3256-2-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\"><div id=\"panel-3256-2-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\"><div class=\"textwidget\"><p><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">A BIG THANK YOU to AAA of Oregon/Beaverton for their generosity. Providing their parking lot year after year to RHBA for our Annual Recycle/Shred Event.</span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Friends of West Slope Library Association and Garden Home Community Library: Collecting bottles and cans</li>\n<li>Neighborhood House: Collecting non-perishable food and personal hygiene items. (Statistics: 1.2 lbs of food = 1 meal according to the Oregon Food Bank).</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-3256-2-1\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\"><div id=\"panel-3256-2-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"3\"><div class=\"textwidget\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-3132\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025-12inx24in-Minicade-Event-Sponsors-150x300.jpg\" alt=\"sponsor thank you image\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025-12inx24in-Minicade-Event-Sponsors-150x300.jpg 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025-12inx24in-Minicade-Event-Sponsors-512x1024.jpg 512w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025-12inx24in-Minicade-Event-Sponsors-768x1536.jpg 768w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025-12inx24in-Minicade-Event-Sponsors-1024x2048.jpg 1024w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025-12inx24in-Minicade-Event-Sponsors-100x200.jpg 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025-12inx24in-Minicade-Event-Sponsors-200x400.jpg 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025-12inx24in-Minicade-Event-Sponsors-300x600.jpg 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025-12inx24in-Minicade-Event-Sponsors-450x900.jpg 450w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025-12inx24in-Minicade-Event-Sponsors-600x1200.jpg 600w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025-12inx24in-Minicade-Event-Sponsors-900x1800.jpg 900w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025-12inx24in-Minicade-Event-Sponsors.jpg 1152w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\"></p>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-3256-2-2\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\"><div id=\"panel-3256-2-2-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"4\"><div class=\"textwidget\">\n<ul>\n<li>Community Warehouse: A nonprofit furniture bank in Portland, Tigard and Gresham that collects home goods and redistributes them to those who need them most.</li>\n<li>Valley Community Presbyterian Church Earth Care Team had a steady flow of donations. They will be at a separate location (a few blocks away) collecting other recyclable items, same day.</li>\n</ul>\n\n</div></div></div></div></div>\t"
}